      "patchset_number": 1,
      "line": 98,
      "message": "All these must be constants. Even here in this code you're using them twice. In general this long row of put()'s and remove()'s looks ugly. Let's think how to make this code cleaner. \n\nAlso, try not to invent the name but re-use the ones that are being already used in logback.xml - it will make changing the configuration later easier (or won't be even required).",
