      "patchset_number": 4,
      "line": 39,
      "message": "I think you might be right prefixing these with something distinguishable. Let's introduce a prefix, and then add it to the constants. Example:\nprivate static final String PREFIX = \"onap.log.\";\nprivate static final String BEGIN_TIMESTAMP = PREFIX + \"BeginTimestamp\" and so on.\nBTW, I believe this same prefix should be shared with the implementation of context service.",
